==English==

===Noun===
'''parasite'''
# A (generally undesirable) living organism that exists by stealing the resources needed by another (generally desirable) living organism. See [[flea]], [[tick]], [[mite]].
# {{pejorative}} a useless person who always relies on other people's work and gives nothing back.

